	 Length/N,Angle/N,Blend/N,CenterX/N,CenterY/N,OuterRad/N,InnerR
	 ad/N,AntiAlias/S

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
      Run the PolarBlur hook.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
      @{u}Length@{uu}
	 Length of the blur.

      @{u}Angle@{uu}
	 Angle of the blur (0-360).

      @{u}Blend@{uu}
	 Blend percentage (0-100).

      @{u}CenterX, CenterY@{uu}
	 Center point of the effect.  Defaults to the center of the
	 image.

      @{u}OuterRad, InnerRad@{uu}
	 Outer and inner radius of the effect, in pixels.  Defaults to
	 affecting the entire image.

      @{u}AntiAlias@{uu}
	 If specified, the effect is anti-aliased.

   @{b}RESULT@{ub}
      None.

@endnode

@node HookPolarMosaic "Hook PolarMosaic"

HOOK POLARMOSAIC (2.0)

   @{b}FORMAT@{ub}
      Hook PolarMosaic
	 Slices/N,Tracks/N,Angle/N,Blend/N,CenterX/N,CenterY/N,OuterRad
	 /N,InnerRad/N,AntiAlias/S,HighQuality/S,LowQuality/S,NoPrep/S

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
      Run the PolarMosaic hook.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
      @{u}Slices, Tracks@{uu}
	 Slices and tracks to use.

      @{u}Angle@{uu}
	 Angle of the mosaic pattern (0-360).

      @{u}Blend@{uu}
	 Blend percentage (0-100).

      @{u}CenterX, CenterY@{uu}
	 Center position of the effect in pixels.  Defaults to the
	 center of the image.

      @{u}OuterRad, InnerRad@{uu}
	 Outer and inner radius of the effect in pixels.  Defaults to
	 the entire image.

      @{u}AntiAlias@{uu}
	 If set, performs anti-aliasing.

      @{u}HighQuality, LowQuality, NoPrep@{uu}
	 Level of quality of the effect.  If not specified, the normal
	 quality is used.

   @{b}RESULT@{ub}
      None.

