@node HookRadialStar "Hook RadialStar"

HOOK RADIALSTAR (2.0)

   @{b}FORMAT@{ub}
      Hook RadialStar
	 Radius/N,Points/N,Thickness/N,Angle/N,Blend/N,Color/N,CenterX/
	 N,CenterY/N,CoronaRadius/N,CoronaBlend/N,CoronaThick/N,CoronaC
	 olor/N,GlowRadius/N,Add/S,Fade/S,Light/S,TaperIn/S,TaperOut/S,
	 Flare/S

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
      Run the RadialStar hook.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
      @{u}Radius@{uu}
	 Radius of the star, in pixels.

      @{u}Points@{uu}
	 Number of points in the star.

      @{u}Thickness@{uu}
	 Thickness of each point, in pixels.

      @{u}Angle@{uu}
	 Angle of rotation of the star, in degrees.  Positive angles
	 rotate clockwise, while negative angles rotate counter-
	 clockwise.  Default 0.

      @{u}Blend@{uu}
	 Blend percentage (0 - 100).  Default 100.

      @{u}Color@{uu}
	 Color to use to generate the star.  0 (the default) uses the
	 current drawing color; values from 1-8 use that color range.

      @{u}CenterX, CenterY@{uu}
	 Center of the star, in pixels.  Defaults to the center of the
	 image.

      @{u}CoronaRadius@{uu}
	 Radius of the corona, in pixels.

      @{u}CoronaBlend@{uu}
	 Blend percentage of the corona (0-100).

      @{u}CoronaThick@{uu}
	 Thickness of the corona, in pixels.

      @{u}CoronaColor@{uu}
	 Color to use in generating the corona.  0 (the default) uses
	 the current drawing color; values from 1-8 use that color
	 range.

      @{u}GlowRadius@{uu}
	 Radius of the glow, in pixels.

      @{u}Add@{uu}
	 Add switch.

      @{u}Fade@{uu}
	 Fade switch.

      @{u}Light@{uu}
	 Light switch.

      @{u}TaperIn, TaperOut, Flare@{uu}
	 Specifies the mode of operation.  Defaults to Normal.

   @{b}RESULT@{ub}
      None.

@endnode

